# codebase-memory-mcp ignore (gitignore syntax). Keeps the knowledge graph to real
# source — exclude throwaway generated output the indexer would otherwise ingest.

# Generated benchmark fixtures: one-off tsc projects regenerated by `pnpm bench`,
# already in .gitignore. ~9.5k nodes of noise (generated mixin classes) if indexed.
bench/fixtures/generated/

# Compiled output of the nested fixture suites (their dist/ isn't covered by the
# root dist hardcode because it's a nested path).
tests/fixture-suite/dist/
tests/declaration-fixture-suite/dist/
